        <h2>General</h2>
        <p>These Terms are subject to occasional revision. Any changes to these Terms will be effective upon the earliest of thirty (30) calendar days following our dispatch of an e-mail notice to you or thirty (30) calendar days following our posting of notice of the changes on our Site.</p>

